ael-news/holylandings/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/i-was-afraid-to-tell-my-holocaust-survivor-friend-i-was-going-to-germany/00000191-c251-d549-a9ff-e371c8bf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第335天：埃及军事首长对加沙边境进行突击检查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-335-egypts-military-chief-holds-surprise-inspection-of-gaza-border/00000191-c31b-df27-a9b9-fb9bd3560000</link><description>美国官员告诉记者，以色列和哈马斯同意 90% 的停火条款 ■ 美国驻以色列特使卢驳斥了内塔尼亚胡关于拟议停战协议第一阶段要求以色列从费城走廊撤军的说法 ■ 国际刑事法院首席检察官卡里姆·汗国防部长加兰特表示，对内塔尼亚胡发出搜查令的请求是基于他亲自审查的证据 ■ 这是战争开始 335 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-335-egypts-military-chief-holds-surprise-inspection-of-gaza-border/00000191-c31b-df27-a9b9-fb9bd3560000</guid></item><item><title>对以色列占领加沙的恐惧促使埃及与土耳其走得更近</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/fear-of-potential-occupation-of-gaza-pushes-egypt-closer-to-turkey/00000191-c28e-d09f-ab91-de9ef0280000</link><description>开罗仍然被认为是美国推动的反伊朗联盟的重要组成部分，但随着对以色列的批评不断增加，这一防御屏障正在崩溃</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:11:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/fear-of-potential-occupation-of-gaza-pushes-egypt-closer-to-turkey/00000191-c28e-d09f-ab91-de9ef0280000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为何不起诉哈马斯 10 月 7 日暴行的嫌疑人？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-delaying-indictments-of-oct-7-suspects-over-open-legal-questions/00000191-c2a2-d2ba-adb1-e6ab30800000</link><description>美国联邦当局已对哈马斯高级官员提出指控，但在以色列，对数千名巴勒斯坦嫌疑人的起诉却被推迟。从国际法考虑到以色列人质的命运，以下是尚未提出指控的原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 15:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-delaying-indictments-of-oct-7-suspects-over-open-legal-questions/00000191-c2a2-d2ba-adb1-e6ab30800000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡失态后，以色列重申摩洛哥对西撒哈拉的主权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-reaffirms-moroccan-sovereignty-of-western-sahara-after-netanyahu-gaffe/00000191-c25b-d870-a59d-e67b87690000</link><description>在新闻发布会上，内塔尼亚胡展示了一张大型中东和北非数字地图，其中摩洛哥南部被标记为西撒哈拉。以色列于 2023 年承认摩洛哥对争议领土的主权，以换取恢复外交关系</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 15:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-reaffirms-moroccan-sovereignty-of-western-sahara-after-netanyahu-gaffe/00000191-c25b-d870-a59d-e67b87690000</guid></item><item><title>瑞安航空暂停以色列航班至 10 月 26 日，跳过高需求假期季节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-halts-israel-flights-until-october-26-skipping-high-demand-holiday-season/00000191-c230-d2ba-adb1-e6b98bdc0000</link><description>德国汉莎航空将于周四恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班；对于消费者来说，瑞安航空的决定将减少假期期间的航班供应，可能会推高机票价格</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:26:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-halts-israel-flights-until-october-26-skipping-high-demand-holiday-season/00000191-c230-d2ba-adb1-e6b98bdc0000</guid></item><item><title>“时间不多了；美国驻以色列特使在人质协议推动中警告称，将没有生命可救</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/there-wont-be-lives-left-to-save-u-s-envoy-to-israel-warns-in-hostage-deal-push/00000191-c1e4-dd1b-a7db-f7fef14f0000</link><description>卢大使反驳了内塔尼亚胡关于以色列国防军从加沙和费城走廊全面撤军是协议初始阶段的一部分的说法：“协议中没有提到费城走廊；起草框架时甚至没有考虑到这一点”</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 11:35:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/there-wont-be-lives-left-to-save-u-s-envoy-to-israel-warns-in-hostage-deal-push/00000191-c1e4-dd1b-a7db-f7fef14f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡受到全球谴责，忙于躲避破坏人质交易的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/rattled-by-global-rebuke-netanyahu-scrambles-to-fend-off-charges-of-sabotaging-gaza-deal/00000191-c140-d2e0-a7d5-ddd270f10000</link><description>除了与外媒举行新闻发布会外，内塔尼亚胡还派了自己的心腹罗恩·德尔默前往美国媒体讨论人质谈判，因为总理担心美国媒体会更多地关注人质家属对他的批评</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 10:34:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/rattled-by-global-rebuke-netanyahu-scrambles-to-fend-off-charges-of-sabotaging-gaza-deal/00000191-c140-d2e0-a7d5-ddd270f10000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，大多数以色列人支持审查加沙战争社交媒体帖子，揭露犹太与阿拉伯之间的分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/poll-majority-of-israelis-back-censoring-gaza-war-posts-exposing-jewish-arab-divide/00000191-c119-de0a-afd5-d959c4d20000</link><description>民意调查发现，政治分歧进一步影响了对审查制度的看法。在以色列右翼人士中，76% 的人希望封锁支持加沙平民的帖子，而左翼人士中只有 25% 的人愿意</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 09:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/poll-majority-of-israelis-back-censoring-gaza-war-posts-exposing-jewish-arab-divide/00000191-c119-de0a-afd5-d959c4d20000</guid></item><item><title>卡梅尔·盖特的家人授权播放哈马斯被囚禁的视频：“内塔尼亚胡判处她死刑”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/carmel-gats-family-authorizes-airing-captivity-video-netanyahu-sentenced-her-to-death/00000191-c0a9-dffe-abf9-fdff26310000</link><description>39 岁的盖特 (Gat) 来自贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri)，于 10 月 7 日被绑架。获释的人质称，她主持瑜伽和冥想课程，以帮助他们保持理智。她计划在人质协议的初始阶段被释放</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 06:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/carmel-gats-family-authorizes-airing-captivity-video-netanyahu-sentenced-her-to-death/00000191-c0a9-dffe-abf9-fdff26310000</guid></item><item><title>“哈里斯同情亲哈马斯的民主党人”：副总统拜登在共和党犹太会议上抨击以色列政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/on-first-night-of-gop-jewish-confab-speakers-assail-biden-and-harris-over-israel-policies/00000191-c02b-d2e0-a7d5-ddfb24a30000</link><description>拉斯维加斯共和党犹太大会的代表们指责现任政府为哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击提供了便利，让反犹太主义在国内愈演愈烈，并且未能勇敢地面对伊朗</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 03:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/on-first-night-of-gop-jewish-confab-speakers-assail-biden-and-harris-over-israel-policies/00000191-c02b-d2e0-a7d5-ddfb24a30000</guid></item><item><title>数百人抬着棺材在特拉维夫游行，悼念被杀的以色列人质；白宫：哈马斯是协议的障碍</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article-live/u-s-can-ensure-israeli-security-if-idf-withdraws-from-philadelphi-route-official-says/00000191-bffd-d26b-abfd-bfff57690000</link><description>国际刑事法院首席检察官为内塔尼亚胡、勇敢逮捕令辩护：“我已经看到证据” ■ 慕尼黑袭击以色列领事馆：枪手是当局已知的伊斯兰分子 ■ 以色列国防军：向以色列北部发射火箭弹和八架无人机；无人员伤亡 ■ 加沙卫生部：以色列拒绝协调医疗队入境进行脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种 ■ 美国高级官员：如果以色列国防军从费城撤军，我们可以确保以色列的安全</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 02:31:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article-live/u-s-can-ensure-israeli-security-if-idf-withdraws-from-philadelphi-route-official-says/00000191-bffd-d26b-abfd-bfff57690000</guid></item><item><title>杀死疑似小偷的基布兹安全小组成员不会面临审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-security-squad-member-who-killed-suspected-thief-wont-face-trial/00000191-bf0b-d2e0-a7d5-bfdb3da80000</link><description>检察官结案，称有证据支持枪手在射杀一名持刀的贝都因青年时出于自卫的说法。受害人家属表示将上诉</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 22:07:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-security-squad-member-who-killed-suspected-thief-wont-face-trial/00000191-bf0b-d2e0-a7d5-bfdb3da80000</guid></item><item><title>被释放的人质敦促以色列总统谴责内塔尼亚胡的玩忽职守</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/former-hostage-urges-israeli-president-to-call-out-netanyahus-dereliction-of-duty/00000191-bef7-d9c6-a997-beff55930000</link><description>利亚特·阿齐利在前总统西蒙·佩雷斯的官方纪念仪式上发表讲话：“内塔尼亚胡反对我们支持人质协议的以色列公民，并将我们视为威胁——这是他政治生存所需的毒药。”我们是一个被内外破坏者绑架的国家”</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 21:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/former-hostage-urges-israeli-president-to-call-out-netanyahus-dereliction-of-duty/00000191-bef7-d9c6-a997-beff55930000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中丧生的一个以色列家庭的四名成员在贝埃里基布兹安息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/four-members-of-one-israeli-family-killed-on-october-7-laid-to-rest-in-kibbutz-beeri/00000191-be6a-dd1b-a7db-bffe74000000</link><description>10 月 7 日被谋杀的 Heztroni 家族的四名成员被重新安葬在贝埃里基布兹：12 岁的双胞胎 Liel 和 Yanai，以及抚养他们的年迈的祖父母 Ayala 和 Avia</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 19:51:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/four-members-of-one-israeli-family-killed-on-october-7-laid-to-rest-in-kibbutz-beeri/00000191-be6a-dd1b-a7db-bffe74000000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯并不是以色列内部裂痕的始作俑者，分裂也不仅仅是外部敌人造成的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-04/ty-article/.highlight/how-to-stop-peaceniks-from-falling-into-hamas-trap-of-holding-israeli-leaders-to-account/00000191-be0c-de0a-afd5-fe4c2b510000</link><description>毫无疑问，哈马斯利用人质进行宣传。但内塔尼亚胡所说的哈马斯利用内部分歧在以色列制造分裂并不是哈马斯的发明，这种分裂不仅仅是外部敌人造成的</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 19:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-04/ty-article/.highlight/how-to-stop-peaceniks-from-falling-into-hamas-trap-of-holding-israeli-leaders-to-account/00000191-be0c-de0a-afd5-fe4c2b510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家档案馆直到 2089 年才会披露内塔尼亚胡寄出的信件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-state-archives-wont-reveal-letters-sent-by-netanyahu-until-2089/00000191-be0f-dc3b-a7df-ff5f24fd0000</link><description>档案馆以隐私问题为由，密封了内塔尼亚胡写给多位知名人士的私人信件，尽管此前已批准公开类似的信件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:33:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-state-archives-wont-reveal-letters-sent-by-netanyahu-until-2089/00000191-be0f-dc3b-a7df-ff5f24fd0000</guid></item><item><title>伴随脊髓灰质炎疫苗进入加沙的阴谋论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/the-conspiracy-theory-accompanying-the-polio-vaccine-into-gaza/00000191-bdfc-dd1b-a7db-bffe3f160000</link><description>备受瞩目的加沙活动家 Bisan Owda 并不信任以色列已经签署的脊髓灰质炎疫苗。但包括医疗专业人士在内的许多网上人士建议这位获得艾美奖提名的网红删除她的视频并道歉，以免小儿麻痹症在拉斯维加斯大道蔓延</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:16:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/the-conspiracy-theory-accompanying-the-polio-vaccine-into-gaza/00000191-bdfc-dd1b-a7db-bffe3f160000</guid></item></channel></rss>